        <abstract>
            <p>Division of CW’s share [of E. A. Darwin’s estate]. Investment advice.</p>
            <p>Recounts his memories of their mother and of her death. Remembers "her black velvet gown and her work table and the death scene", but cannot remember her face. Remembers that Caroline "always acted like a mother" to him and Catherine.</p>
        </abstract>
